Add this to the end of your externals file:
http://source.opencastproject.org/svn/contrib/captions/trunk/opencast-captionsHandler-service-impl     opencast-captionsHandler-service-impl

Update the modules in the pom.xml as indicated at https://wiki.opencastproject.org/confluence/display/open/Create+a+New+Service:
add these to the modules listing:
    <module>opencast-captionsHandler-service-impl</module>

Do a normal rebuild and redeploy and restart sequence and the captions handler service endpoints should appear at matterhorn root url (http://{server}/).
